---
title: صفحه مورد نظر یافت نشد
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<header class="page-header" x-data>
  <button class="icon-btn" @click="history.back();">
    {% alwatrIcon "arrow-forward" %}
  </button>
  <h1>{{ config.siteName }}</h1>
</header>

<main class="main-container">
  <article
    class="max-w-screen-medium mx-auto rounded-xl border border-outlineVariant border-opacity-50 p-4 text-center shadow-sm"
  >
    <div>
      <div class="text-[3rem]">{% alwatrIcon "frame_inspect" %}</div>
      <div class="mt-4 text-titleMedium">متاسفانه صفحه مورد نظر یافت نشد!</div>
      <p class="text-secondary mt-2">
        صفحه‌ای که به دنبال آن بودید یافت نشد. لطفاً از منوی استفاده کنید.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/"
        class="mx-auto mt-6 flex h-10 cursor-pointer select-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary px-2 transition-opacity elevation-0 state-onPrimary hover:elevation-1 active:elevation-0 aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:opacity-40"
      >
        {% alwatrIcon "home", "text-[1.125rem]" %}
        <span class="px-2 text-labelLarge">بازگشت به صفحه اصلی</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/fa/contact.html"
        class="mx-auto mt-2 flex h-10 cursor-pointer select-none items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primaryContainer px-2 transition-opacity elevation-0 state-onPrimaryContainer hover:elevation-1 active:elevation-0 aria-disabled:pointer-events-none aria-disabled:opacity-40"
      >
        {% alwatrIcon "headset_mic", "text-[1.125rem]" %}
        <span class="px-2 text-labelLarge">ارتباط با ما</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </article>
</main>
